  rJava (>= 1.0-6),
  RProtoBuf (>= 0.4.20),
  rjd3toolkit (>= 3.7.1),
  rjd3xjars (>= 0.1.0),
  checkmate,
  forecast,
  methods
SystemRequirements: Java (>= 17)
